{"tid":614918,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 人生必睇電影","createTime":"2018-04-03T03:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T05:38:32.000Z","uid":42058,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2fde54285aaeafefcbeb67347c388d8dc9f330","tid":614918,"uid":42058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"小弟非常鐘意睇戲 想分享下D我認為出色既電影 雖然未必岩每個人口味 但都希望有興趣既巴打都可以留低討論下 分享更多好睇既電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(排名唔分先後)<br />\n<br />\n1.Batman - The Dark Knight<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/101357_52d453cc17e17fbe537b4cf2cb7d23d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F101357_52d453cc17e17fbe537b4cf2cb7d23d3.jpg&h=a980410e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至今最深刻既英雄電影 優秀既反派<br />\nJoker 出色演技加上精湛劇本 造就令人恐懼同有威脅力既反派 <br />\n電影當中帶出好多值得深思既問題 英雄責任 人性 哲學 <br />\n睇完令人好大感受 未睇既巴打要去睇 睇完既巴打就再去睇多次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. No Country for Old Men <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/104217_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F104217_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=f5b5fc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n07年既作品 當時拎左奧斯卡四個獎 最佳影片 導演 男配角 改編劇本 <br />\n一開始我都係因為反派先係接觸呢套戲 但睇完之後 發覺套戲更令人細味 同時顛覆我對電影既諗法 (唔劇透太多) 有興趣自己睇<br />\n<br />\n3.Logan<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/105247_2b3037682c0470c9f041a53d0d676cac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F105247_2b3037682c0470c9f041a53d0d676cac.jpg&h=32d785fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老實話我係未睇過X-men 系列但係走左去睇 Logan 啦 以我既記憶 我就只係睇過狼人前傳(變有金鋼爪個集) 我唔理咩世界觀 以獨立電影黎睇 呢套真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n就連無睇過Xmen 既我都可以比呢套野感動到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成套野無帶出咩意義 但睇得出導演好著重情感 成套戲都好人性化 好感受到愛 所以......想入去喊既巴打可以去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a094e6d143b400f81157bb86d768ee94fedfd1","tid":614918,"uid":23833,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"阿甘故事<br />\n<br />\n機場客運站"},{"pid":"1ee750c545ca4d0184d937af6e36bb2f2b8dfb14","tid":614918,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"Into the wild"},{"pid":"b49d7bb29a867d17a90c87ce9a79a01816d1a1c1","tid":614918,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"浩劫重生 韋信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd44258aa7d60e396363d4dd551deab25d92bef5","tid":614918,"uid":112523,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"The Shining<br />\n<br />\n因為前幾日睇完Ready Player One，入面有Part係講The Shining，跟手啦啦聲返屋企睇返，終於明D人點解咁中意stanley kubrick。"},{"pid":"3459686c01895620b6ecf5edd2168b7b568a00f8","tid":614918,"uid":116530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/111108_3c751b7a4356074ff570b5fa87a17a12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F111108_3c751b7a4356074ff570b5fa87a17a12.png&h=460f3ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b61a744a6505a6d4fbbbe3ed6c5cb769d911fdb7","tid":614918,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"美國隊長1"},{"pid":"da3b2e684c30b56492e18be52eba3956eef2931d","tid":614918,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"作死不離三兄妹"},{"pid":"8ec87141544da0d7ce49aabfa33c82762a5e7c9b","tid":614918,"uid":171426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"香港製造"},{"pid":"c6b2bb1e4a7c56ccb75c9e93b11763459a7301df","tid":614918,"uid":80696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ba0c4f14619e016c7773155023a20a9fbca2a6","tid":614918,"uid":42058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"4.Interstellar<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/110531_baed64444788eefc67173244c58d836c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F110531_baed64444788eefc67173244c58d836c.jpg&h=6d710667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個陣入戲院睇 畫面真係好靚 有好好既劇本 (雖然有人話佢抄多啦A夢電影)<br />\n都係主打親情 最尾結局都會眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5.一念無明<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/110955_971715b7c4e2efa3c7f2d069e17561ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F110955_971715b7c4e2efa3c7f2d069e17561ad.jpg&h=51a5d899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多巴打可能會覺得 &quot;香港電影？不了。&quot; <br />\n咁香港電影雖然未話真係好到可以同出面比 資金都唔夠外國多 <br />\n但係好多次香港電影都有佢特別既野 要生活係香港文化先睇得明 <br />\n呢套唔係話咩人生必睇 <br />\n不過我認為生活係香港既人都可以睇下 套戲講左好多香港問題 例如香港少有人關心既情緒問題 住屋等等 <br />\n只可以話係 香港人先會睇得明同睇完有好大感受既戲 有興趣既巴打都可以睇下"},{"pid":"ddf4d98f74b64f2c60ebb449d493ac2159fc4999","tid":614918,"uid":42058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b49d7bb29a867d17a90c87ce9a79a01816d1a1c1","tid":614918,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"浩劫重生 韋信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"呢套好慘 最尾咁辛苦番黎 老婆又嫁左比第個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2717cc3c50d24364c01cafe03fc5db0047d7221","tid":614918,"uid":42058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3459686c01895620b6ecf5edd2168b7b568a00f8","tid":614918,"uid":116530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/111108_3c751b7a4356074ff570b5fa87a17a12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F111108_3c751b7a4356074ff570b5fa87a17a12.png&h=460f3ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"佢呀爸呀媽食到變左做隻豬 我到宜家都記得 童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fd1aaca8602c9eee7f0c0e7ac163390a896b37","tid":614918,"uid":10325,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"勁抽福祿壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94accfbd93600387cf74362a567644c1aaa16a8","tid":614918,"uid":42058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"Slumdog Millionaire<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/112548_8de9d2133785545789988de53d6c4fe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F112548_8de9d2133785545789988de53d6c4fe4.jpg&h=8a42263a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中文譯名可能會為人熟悉d 一百萬零一夜<br />\n講一個住貧民窟既細路 未讀過書 去參加陳啟泰既節目 好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5da36629f13682c1bed70e1248329abe23d63ad","tid":614918,"uid":54492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"香水"},{"pid":"dceb5f5df71394bb6f6328e042e2700be5c86c0b","tid":614918,"uid":42058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc